psidev.psi.mi.jami.enricher.listener

Interface OntologyTermEnricherListener

  • All Superinterfaces:
    AliasesChangeListener<CvTerm>, AnnotationsChangeListener<CvTerm>, CvTermChangeListener, CvTermEnricherListener<OntologyTerm>, EnricherListener<OntologyTerm>, EventListener, IdentifiersChangeListener<CvTerm>, OntologyTermChangeListener, XrefsChangeListener<CvTerm>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    OntologyTermEnricherListenerManager, OntologyTermEnricherLogger, OntologyTermEnricherStatisticsWriter

    public interface OntologyTermEnricherListener
extends CvTermEnricherListener<OntologyTerm>, OntologyTermChangeListener
    An extension of the OntologyTermChangeListener with specific methods related to the process of enriching. Each method will be fired after the change has been made to the ontology term
    Since:
    13/06/13
    Author:
